<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فِي كِتَابِ الْبُغَاةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَإِذَا أَمَرَ الْقَائِدُ سَرِيَّةً مِنَ الْجَيْشِ بِالإِْغَارَةِ عَلَى الْعَدُوِّ، فَمَا غَنِمَتْهُ هَذِهِ السَّرِيَّةُ شَارَكَهَا الْجَيْشُ فِي هَذِهِ الْغَنِيمَةِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> . وَقَدْ ذَكَرَ ذَلِكَ الْفُقَهَاءُ فِي كِتَابِ الْغَنِيمَةِ مِنْ كُتُبِ الْفِقْهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>اغْتِرَارٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> تَغْرِيرٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>اغْتِسَالٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> غُسْلٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>اغْتِيَالٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">اُنْظُرْ:</span> غِيلَةٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>إِغْرَاءٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">التَّعْرِيفُ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - الإِْغْرَاءُ مَصْدَرُ أَغْرَى،<span class="c5"> وَأَغْرَى بِالشَّيْءِ:</span> أُولِعَ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
